data.description: Introducing the Captiva II model, a 2021 Seagate home that surpasses new builds. This meticulously maintained property boasts an array of custom upgrades. Enjoy a contemporary open floor plan with sleek tile flooring throughout - no carpets. The kitchen and bathroom feature modern quartz countertops, complemented by 42'' upper solid wood cabinetry with crown molding. Samsung stainless steel appliances add a touch of sophistication. The laundry room is enhanced with a convenient washtub and storage cabinets. Step onto the covered porch, offering  space for outdoor dining and grilling. The fully fenced yard includes an access gate and above ground pool.  A lawn irrigation system with well eliminates the need for costly city water for landscaping. Just two years old, this home is in impeccable condition and awaits a new owner. Don't miss the opportunity for a timely purchase!
